aom.scripting.ui.console

Class Console

  • Object
    • Console

  • public abstract class Console
extends Object
    This class provides a collection of Console commands that don't fit in any of the subcategories.
    Editor Mode Only
    Some console commands only run in editor mode. Use the following template to make them work: 
     subModeEnter("Simulation", "Editor");
 //your editor command here;
 subModeLeave("Simulation", "Editor");
 modeEnter("pregame");
 modeEnter("Simulation");
 subModeEnter("Simulation", "Singleplayer");
    Author
    Mythic_Freak - mythic.freak[a]gmail.com

       string context,

        Maps an input event to the given command, in the given context.
        Parameters:
        key -
        context -

        General contexts:

        • root
        • developer //needs +developer in user.cfg
        • aiDebug //needs +aiDebug in user.cfg
        • pregame
        • world //game + editor (basically everything with a map in it)
        • game
        • postgame
        • editor
        • strategicmap //the big map when you press tab in AoT
        • console
        • XSDebugger
        • arena //weird campaign menu
        • AILocSelect

        • buildAccel
        • settlementAccel
